Package CCDD

Class CcddPy4JScriptEngine

java.lang.Object
CCDD.CcddPy4JScriptEngine
All Implemented Interfaces:
ScriptEngine
class CcddPy4JScriptEngine extends Object implements ScriptEngine
CFS Command and Data Dictionary Py4J script engine class. This class handles script engine calls and allows the API to treat Py4J as a JSR-223 compliant scripting language
